FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FIt is unclear how Nord, linked to
OL,8,FRussian oligarch Alexey Mordashov,
OL,9,Fgained permission to pass through the
OL,10,Fwaterway, of which Iran has continued
OL,11,Fits blockade despite a tentative
OL,12,Fceasefire which began on April 8.
OL,14,FThe US has imposed a blockade of its
OL,15,Fown of Iranian ports and has turned
OL,16,Faway cargo ships and oil tankers in
OL,17,Fresponse to obstruction of shipping by
OL,18,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FIt is not clear if US naval ships
OL,8,Fwould have crossed paths with Nord,
OL,9,Fnor what the military's policy would
OL,10,Fbe if it encountered a private vessel
OL,11,Fowned by a Russian oligarch.
OL,13,FMaritime data from Marinetraffic.com
OL,14,Fshows that Nord arrived at the Al Mouj
OL,15,Fmarina in Muscat, Oman, on Sunday
OL,16,Fmorning, having reportedly crossed the
OL,17,FStrait on Saturday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
