CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FHis net worth is estimated to be $36.9
OL,8,Fbillion (around #27.3 billion), making
OL,9,Fhim the 58th richest person in the
OL,10,Fworld, according to Forbes, and he has
OL,11,Fbeen hailed as one of the richest
OL,12,Fpeople in Russia.
OL,14,FHe is also chairman of investment firm
OL,15,FSevergroup, which holds stakes in many
OL,16,Findustries including steel (including
OL,17,FSeverstal), telecoms, consumer goods,
OL,18,Fpower engineering and medicine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
