PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FIn 2024, Severgroup acquired the
OL,8,FCordiant group, one of Russia's
OL,9,Fleading manufacturers of tyres, auto
OL,10,Fcomponents, thermal equipment and
OL,11,Fpower tools.
OL,13,FMordashov also has close links to the
OL,14,FRussian government and is described by
OL,15,Fsanctions database provider
OL,16,FOpenSanctions as being part of
OL,17,FPresident Vladimir Putin's "closest
OL,18,Fcircle".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
