PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FThe fact that he was one of 37 Russian
OL,8,Fbusinesspeople who met with Putin in
OL,9,FFebruary 2022 to discuss the impact of
OL,10,FWestern sanctions following the launch
OL,11,Fof the Ukraine war demonstrates his
OL,12,Fclose ties to the president.
OL,14,FHe was also among the leading Russian
OL,15,Fbusiness figures who participated in
OL,16,Fthe congress of the Russian Union of
OL,17,FIndustrialists and Entrepreneurs in
OL,18,FMarch 2023, where Putin urged
OL,19,Fbillionaires to put "patriotism before
OL,20,Fprofit".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
