CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FMordashov's business empire supplies
OL,8,Farmoured steel used by the Russian
OL,9,Fmilitary, connecting him directly to
OL,10,Fthe war in Ukraine.
OL,12,FHe is subject to sanctions by the US,
OL,13,Fthe European Union and the UK. This
OL,14,Fled to another one of his yachts, the
OL,15,FLady M, valued at 65 million euros
OL,16,F(around #56 million), being seized by
OL,17,Fauthorities in Italy in March 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
