OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FShe has a cruising speed of 15.0kn
OL,8,F(about 17.3mph) and a top speed of
OL,9,F20.0kn (about 23mph), making her
OL,10,Ffaster than average yachts of her size.
OL,12,FShe has not just one, but two
OL,13,Fhelipads, one of which is on the bow
OL,14,Fand another on the bridge deck aft,
OL,15,Fwhich is covered by a retractable
OL,16,Fhangar.
OL,18,FNord's helicopter hangar converts to a
OL,19,Fglass-sided squash court when not in
OL,20,Fuse, according to Yachtbuyer.com.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FThe yacht also features a 25 metre-
OL,8,Flong swimming pool, a gym, a spa,
OL,9,Fsauna, a dedicated beauty salon and a
OL,10,Fcinema.
OL,12,FShe also has an ice-class hull,
OL,13,Fmeaning she is capable of navigating
OL,14,Fthrough icy Arctic waters.
OL,16,FNord's interior and exterior was
OL,17,Fdesigned by Italian studio Nuvolari-
OL,18,FLenard and she was constructed by
OL,19,FGerman shipbuilder Lurssen.
OL,26,@{D@Uxz
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
