CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1777392671
OL,3,CWho is the Russian oligarch whose
OL,4,Cyacht passed through the Strait of
OL,5,CHormuz?
OL,7,FShe originally flew a Cayman Islands
OL,8,Fflag in 2021, but her registration was
OL,9,Fchanged to being Russian-flagged in
OL,10,FJune 2022.
OL,12,FWhile for all intents and purposes,
OL,13,FMordashov is the owner of the yacht,
OL,14,Freports suggest the vessel is
OL,15,Fregistered to a Russian company owned
OL,16,Fby the oligarch's wife in the town of
OL,17,FCherepovets, where Severstal is also
OL,18,Fregistered.
OL,20,FITV News has contacted representatives
OL,21,Fof Mordashov for comment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
